# Prompt Hub collaboration rules

- Start with `docs/PROJECT_CONTEXT.md`, `docs/CURRENT-ISSUES.md`, and `docs/AI-PITFALLS.md`.
- Use `docs/FILE-MAP.md` to locate code; do not restore old monolithic files over split sources.
- Preserve user work and user data. Never delete cards or images to make a test pass.
- Do not commit credentials, real test accounts, user UUIDs, backups, `.wrangler/`, or local env files.
- Root loaders, `legacy/`, `styles/`, `partials/`, and `pack-*.js` are one runtime system. Run `npm run check:predeploy` after frontend changes.
- Run `npm run typecheck` and `npm test` in `server/` after Worker changes.
- Shared sync, image, feed, or storage changes require impact analysis and regression tests; see `docs/ARCHITECTURE-CHANGE-GUARD.md`.
- Production is `https://prompt-hubs.com` with API `https://api.prompt-hubs.com`; `.cn` is compatibility only.
- Keep replies in Simplified Chinese unless the user requests otherwise.
